title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Serious changes are brewing in your life now, even if youre not entirely sure what shape and direction they are taking. Perhaps youre uncomfortable with your current uncertainty as you try to line up all your ducks in a row. You might not even know whether the outcome will turn out in your favor or not. Unfortunately, time spent worrying only distracts you from exploring your various options. Relieve yourself of the pressure to make a fast decision just to choose a path forward. Blending your stamina with your faith empowers you to make the best choices. Transformation rarely happens overnight. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
